{"tid":487982,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔知仲應唔應該揾佢","createTime":"2017-12-03T09:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T08:37:16.000Z","uid":5209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0e5e06376adb7c24372c478a4399cc7bfbd9394e","tid":487982,"uid":5209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"我同佢係同事<br />\n同佢識左只係8個月，但係同佢好夾好啱傾<br />\n咩都可以講一餐，除左面對面傾<br />\n大家返到屋企都會wts傾計<br />\n不過wts傾計，係我大部分時間揾佢<br />\n而每日放工都一齊搭車走<br />\n每個月最少有2次同佢出去一齊食晚飯，<br />\n有睇過戲，有一齊行過出，係得我地2個<br />\n同埋我地成日傾計都痴到好埋，頭掂頭咁<br />\n公司都傳過我同佢有野，不過都無承認<br />\n最近佢出左trip，我有叫佢得閒揾我<br />\n不過佢去左3日，都無揾過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係咪應該揾佢，會唔會阻住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢好似特登唔揾我"},{"pid":"81395575b1048c0c2210eef76b3eaa0461bb384c","tid":487982,"uid":130162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T09:27:36.000Z","msg":"可以收手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585ae56c9fe181e54dd64fd6ff956f722d0465ab","tid":487982,"uid":5209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:12:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以收手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係收得皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3a3338c0342eb56b20e04304ab86a05c7882ba","tid":487982,"uid":52891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:18:58.000Z","msg":"同你做過果啲暖昧野<br />\n佢同時同其他人做緊"},{"pid":"5759b4a359967b530fc5c64497fe10cfb800a86d","tid":487982,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:25:07.000Z","msg":"比人中出左啦"},{"pid":"86cdcb165ea6a0ea218c94acc11937d7456ef5f2","tid":487982,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:33:49.000Z","msg":"表白啦"},{"pid":"5902c583f26fe876311f39c6ea077c1ccaee9a3c","tid":487982,"uid":5209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:41:52.000Z","msg":"就黎痴線<br />\n仲未做到唔在乎佢"},{"pid":"1d550055c5e6f62fcca8b9b86def36937b93d7c8","tid":487982,"uid":120801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0693b4a97144496bc103438493dcde1e989ae0b","tid":487982,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:45:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5417d876c270e198b52c883af01020a3b5ccae71","tid":487982,"uid":113612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:46:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就黎痴線<br />\n仲未做到唔在乎佢</blockquote><br />\n係鐘意你 點會唔掛住你唔搵你 傻仔"},{"pid":"13286843d271f471446f66c2a292397f3b5938a5","tid":487982,"uid":138531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:24:28.000Z","msg":"等佢搵你啦 唔好咁chur"},{"pid":"34c8ee165523b75f16d9a16a0b7a0967bac9674f","tid":487982,"uid":5209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:27:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等佢搵你啦 唔好咁chur</blockquote><br />\n佢唔揾我就代表段關係應該要完<br />\n我仲預備左份聖誕禮物<br />\n都唔知仲俾唔俾佢好<br />\n好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9874800792531407e5df996c8499e0881287c91","tid":487982,"uid":138531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T01:58:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>等佢搵你啦 唔好咁chur</blockquote><br />\n佢唔揾我就代表段關係應該要完<br />\n我仲預備左份聖誕禮物<br />\n都唔知仲俾唔俾佢好<br />\n好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢唔搵你即係對你無意思<br />\n咁你搵佢都無用<br />\n份禮物留番比下個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3984ace1c355e4f2cbdd28e21e8ee4680836cf","tid":487982,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:54:14.000Z","msg":"去旅行有咩好搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咪留言話買左聖誕節禮物俾佢囉"},{"pid":"f02acc0002f729b188c4b7a67d55ec5a0c0e774b","tid":487982,"uid":5209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:57:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>等佢搵你啦 唔好咁chur</blockquote><br />\n佢唔揾我就代表段關係應該要完<br />\n我仲預備左份聖誕禮物<br />\n都唔知仲俾唔俾佢好<br />\n好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢唔搵你即係對你無意思<br />\n咁你搵佢都無用<br />\n份禮物留番比下個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宜家仲未做到唔揾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係咁易"},{"pid":"9edb131a38469a8a0ba972a2e4c74b5fc88de8b5","tid":487982,"uid":5209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:58:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去旅行有咩好搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咪留言話買左聖誕節禮物俾佢囉</blockquote><br />\n佢去快活就唔理我<br />\n係咪代表佢心一直無我既存在"},{"pid":"0ddba2cbc189adef458e566a5426b763caaeb598","tid":487982,"uid":79278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:37:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去旅行有咩好搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咪留言話買左聖誕節禮物俾佢囉</blockquote><br />\n佢去快活就唔理我<br />\n係咪代表佢心一直無我既存在</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}